00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
My king once sought wisdom in such a dharma place.

2
00:00:05,820 --> 00:00:10,820
His son, too, was a disciple of a bodhisattva.

3
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,600
Now I, too, walk on this path.

4
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:17,080
I hope I'm following in my king's steps.

5
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:22,640
Say, my friend, why don't you stay here

6
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:24,360
and tread this path with me?

